{"tid":1467952,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警察謀殺強姦非禮混入同志都唔撚割蓆 學下狗啦","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:45:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T18:09:27.000Z","uid":200493,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e13662be165ffcc8d4ab2b7293acac5e516d29a2","tid":1467952,"uid":200493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:45:39.000Z","msg":"問：阻塞機場搞死香港？<br />\n答：「做法不完美，但可接受，要改善。」<br />\n<br />\n問：點解阻止公安離開？<br />\n答：「佢唔喺現場出現就冇事，去得果度就可能有呢啲風險。」<br />\n<br />\n問：阻止救護帶佢離開？人命嚟㗎。<br />\n答：「而家眾說紛云，我認為事主可以去報警先，警方必定會跟進調查。」<br />\n<br />\n問：點解你地咁冇人性，濫用暴力，究竟想點？<br />\n「在場嘅市民只係用最低武力，當一切平靜後，真誠對話就會展開。」<br />\n<br />\n對唔住，7.21、8.11血仍未乾，有人爆頭，有人失明，有人俾黑警打到成地血都冇收手，之後我從來冇聽過，警方有道歉有撤查。<br />\n<br />\n以上，全部係黑警同林奠嘅對白，香港人已經好克制了。<br />\n<br />\n人命？你睇俾黑警打到成地血嘅義士個樣，同埋呢個公安？現場有一句，喺大陸，你死撚咗啦。<br />\n<br />\n信焉。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#不割席<br />\n#不篤灰<br />\n#不分化<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"707f804a0cc4d51d39e901651e1ec4ecb4adfa6d","tid":1467952,"uid":25866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:45:51.000Z","msg":"請大家入機場前備戰、坐公共交通前就要上裝<br />\n防cctv 因為會有機會好似今日咁打狗救手足<br />\n口罩、帽，仲有耳仔<br />\n全黑衣服、飲水、食野請小心"},{"pid":"e83af6ebaee03a445c3ef5921d415a7e2a668804","tid":1467952,"uid":200493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:47:36.000Z","msg":"推 唔撚割"},{"pid":"5e1bdca7350d96d1f93a11cd8b728d811ffea752","tid":1467952,"uid":200493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,